{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12617, "create_time": 1640072629, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "我觉得这跟碎片化习惯有关系", "timestamp": 1640072629}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12618, "create_time": 1640072664, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "slw", "timestamp": 1640072664}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12628, "create_time": 1640073050, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "多说多表达慢慢就会有进步了。cz建院的，刚入学的时候连思修讨论课都不敢抢发言，后来设计课pre做多了就习惯了，不会紧张了，现在碰到讨论课会抢着发言😋", "timestamp": 1640073050}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12639, "create_time": 1640073331, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "多读书，多思考，多写作，没事就在网络上跟人对对线", "timestamp": 1640073331}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12648, "create_time": 1640073562, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "其实入坑辩论是一种有效提升表达能力的途径，不过我不是很喜欢", "timestamp": 1640073562}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12651, "create_time": 1640073600, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Bob: wow 建院还有这好处", "timestamp": 1640073600}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12682, "create_time": 1640074348, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Carol: 我觉得对于我个人而言，设计课讲方案帮助挺大的，我上过的其他课大部分没有那么密集的口头表达的机会。而且讲方案特别是评图的经历也让我注意表达的逻辑性和条理性，一开始就是东拉西扯，表达不清楚自己的想法", "timestamp": 1640074348}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12733, "create_time": 1640076111, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Bob: 后天就要pre了 有什么分享的吗www", "timestamp": 1640076111}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12804, "create_time": 1640078207, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Carol: 不知道你做的是什么pre。我觉得pre最重要的就是要有逻辑框架，同时要便于听众理解。我本科毕设关于古建的，花了挺多功夫，但是涉及一些专有概念，事先没有解释，然后讲的时候逻辑框架和递进关系也不是很合理吧（因为赶论文来不及花功夫准备😭），然后非古建方向的老师表示虽然知道我做了很多工作，但是他们理解有困难，然后分数也稍微受到了一些影响。确实很多时候展示的效果要比前期做的工作还要重要。\n然后讲的时候也要有重点有取舍吧，事先多排练几次，控制好每部分的时间", "timestamp": 1640078207}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 12907, "create_time": 1640084830, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Bob: 捕捉建院队友一只？", "timestamp": 1640084830}], "create_time": 1640072523, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1640084830, "likenum": 4, "n_attentions": 4, "n_comments": 10, "pid": 4444, "poll": null, "reply": 10, "text": "压力好大啊。\n我跟老师谈话压力都很大。\n想好的话没有说清楚就出来了。\n真羡慕面对领导什么的能自由表达自己想法的人。\n怎么锻炼口才呀www", "timestamp": 1640072523}}